title: Tickets for U2 Croke Park show start at €39 but majority of fans will pay much more
text: Friday 13 January 2017 Tickets for U2 Croke Park show start at €39 but majority of fans will pay much more Eugene Masterson 0 Comments Share Tickets for U2 Croke Park show start at €39 but majority of fans will pay much more Independent.ie U2 may be advertising tickets for their much anticipated Croke Park show this July as starting at a bargain €39 but the vast majority of them will in fact be going on sale for €76. http://www.independent.ie/entertainment/music/music-news/tickets-for-u2-croke-park-show-start-at-39-but-majority-of-fans-will-pay-much-more-35363270.html http://www.independent.ie/incoming/article35351118.ece/c271e/AUTOCROP/h342/3%20NEWS%20PL23369091U2%20pose%20with%20the.jpg U2’s ‘The Joshua Tree’ sold more than 25 million copies.
